{"data":[{"date":"21:19 22/07","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecf ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i to\u00e0n kinh t\u1ebf, Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, Juventus t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y xe h\u01a1i FIAT \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng tho\u00e1i tr\u00e0o khi Ronaldo cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam b\u1ed9n ti\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus, t\u1edd Il Sole 24 Ore th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, &quot;b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&quot; s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 75 \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n v\u00e9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 34 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo c\u00f2n gi\u00fap t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho Juventus. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean kho\u1ea3ng 15% so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1edd v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o, l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn con s\u1ed1 h\u01a1n 200 tri\u1ec7u tr\u00ean Twitter v\u00e0 Instagram g\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCon g\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebb tr\u1ee9ng v\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay trong 24 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Turin, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Juventus b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 520.000 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u, thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 trong top nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramon Calderon, c\u1ef1u Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1t l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng b\u00e1n Ronaldo l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi t\u1eb7ng &quot;con g\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebb tr\u1ee9ng v\u00e0ng&quot; cho Juvetus. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Real Madrid v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/deschamps-cac-hoc-tro-cua-toi-xung-dang-gianh-bong-vang-hon-ronaldo-messi-184-191751.html\">Deschamps: C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ronaldo-cap-ben-turin-juve-co-con-la-juve-389-191603.html\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0&hellip; Juve?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh-188-191598.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo-180-191561.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4505","checkdouble":"191796"},{"date":"22:15 22/07","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/juventus-e.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 d\u1ef1 ICC 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ch\u1ee7 Juventus c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt, danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 t\u1ea1i Hoa K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/juventus-e.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus t\u1ea1i Hoa K\u1ef3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Ronaldo, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m Paulo Dybala, Gonzalo Higuain, Juan Cuadrado, Rodrigo Bentancur v\u00e0 Douglas Costa c\u0169ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t. Nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca (Croatia) v\u00e0 Blaise Matuidi (Ph\u00e1p) s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u1ea3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Juventus t\u1ea1i ICC 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ba tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ICC 2018 g\u1ed3m g\u1eb7p Bayern Munich (6h05 ng\u00e0y 26/7), Benfica (6h05 ng\u00e0y 29/7) v\u00e0 Real Madrid (5h05 ng\u00e0y 5/8).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xen l\u1eabn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn MLS (gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9) di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 6h30 ng\u00e0y 2/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus g\u1ed3m Szczesny, De Sciglio, Chiellini, Benatia, Pjanic, Khedira, Marchisio, Alex Sandro, Caldara, Barzagli, Perin, Joao Cancelo, Pinsoglio, Emre Can, Rugani, Betuatto, Del Favero, Bernardeschi, Fernandes, Macek, Kastanos, Clemenza, Pereira, Beltrame, Favilli, Di Pardo, Fagioli.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus-176-191796.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/deschamps-cac-hoc-tro-cua-toi-xung-dang-gianh-bong-vang-hon-ronaldo-messi-184-191751.html\">Deschamps: C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ronaldo-cap-ben-turin-juve-co-con-la-juve-389-191603.html\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0\u2026 Juve?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh-188-191598.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4504","checkdouble":"191800"},{"date":"21:02 22/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u00f4n vinh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng. S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y Park c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo so bi quay lung neu DT Olympic Viet Nam choi khong tot o ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u0103n tr\u1edf nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Jeong Da-woo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ea7y Park cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng lu\u00f4n mong manh nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tan bi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua \u1edf H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2002&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m c\u0169, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i khi thi\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Palestine v\u00e0 UAE khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y Park th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 theo l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ban \u0111\u1ea7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AFC) m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Theo nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a tin, Indonesia s\u1ebd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai (23/7) nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m c\u1ea3, hai ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u00e0 UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191785.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-lai-asiad-2018-olympic-viet-nam-roi-vao-bang-nao-168-191684.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-292-191650.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/do-hung-dung-mot-net-rat-rieng-cua-nguoi-ha-noi-168-191541.html\">\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng: M\u1ed9t n\u00e9t r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191537.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4503","checkdouble":"191795"},{"date":"21:53 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ai ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean mu\u1ed9n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hai tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 27/7, 13 trong s\u1ed1 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp s\u1ebd l\u00ean mu\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u23 viet nam\" title=\"u23 vi\u1ec7t nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/hlv-le-thuy-hai-nhan-xet-ve-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec b\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA. C\u1ea3 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Trong \u0111\u00f3, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 8 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, SLNA v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u00f2n Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e1m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n g\u1ed3m V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Th\u00e0nh Chung, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. SLNA c\u00f3 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, c\u00f2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i U23<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U23 nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o qu\u00e1 23 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang dau cua DT Olympic Viet Nam tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/bang-asiad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ban \u0111\u1ea7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ban \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Uzbekistan, Bangladesh v\u00e0 Qatar. C\u00f2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n khi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb s\u00f3t l\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0 UAE.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191785.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-lai-asiad-2018-olympic-viet-nam-roi-vao-bang-nao-168-191684.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-292-191650.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/do-hung-dung-mot-net-rat-rieng-cua-nguoi-ha-noi-168-191541.html\">\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng: M\u1ed9t n\u00e9t r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4502","checkdouble":"191799"},{"date":"23:29 22/07","title":"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/8/hlv-tuchel-giuc-rabiot-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Thomas Tuchel hy v\u1ecdng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Adrien Rabiot s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai r\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barcelona.</h2><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Rabiot b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Paulinho ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Rabiot \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a PSG trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern, HLV Tuchel v\u1eabn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/8/hlv-tuchel-giuc-rabiot-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot s\u1edbm quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 Rabiot c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nRabiot \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft PSG b\u1edfi HLV Ancelotti v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 33 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Ligue 1.</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi khuy\u00ean Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Xavi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Rabiot. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Clement Lenglet c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng gia nh\u1eadp Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRabiot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m cho Barca. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabu sao, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c tin \u0111\u1ed3n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 PSG:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/thuyen-truong-psg-nong-long-duoc-lam-viec-voi-mbappe-197-191791.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-31-psg-icc-2018-329-191756.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 3-1 PSG (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4501","checkdouble":"191803"},{"date":"18:46 22/07","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1, Neymar kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 \"thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/bi-chi-trich-an-va-neymar-khong-them-chap-su-thieu-hieu-biet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n k\u1ecbch k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brazil m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 thua B\u1ec9. Theo m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, Neymar v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1ecbu s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec \u201ccon giun x\u00e9o l\u1eafm c\u0169ng qu\u1eb1n\u201d, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Neymar \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi thanh minh cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/neymar-tran-tinh-ve-ly-do-an-va.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mong b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady sao? Kh\u00f4ng, \u0111au l\u1eafm \u0111\u1ea5y. Sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i to\u00e0n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f3 khi \u0111\u1ebfn 4-5 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01b0\u1eddm \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cChuy\u1ec7n n\u00f3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1edfi ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m n\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 coi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a cho m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean Instagram v\u1ec1 video l\u0169 tr\u1ebb b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00ecnh c\u01a1 m\u00e0.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2u th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u2018C\u01b0ng \u00e0, xin l\u1ed7i nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0m \u01a1n tr\u00e1nh ra \u0111\u1ec3 anh ghi b\u00e0n\u2019. \u0110\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2u th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u1eady khi anh ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua, c\u00f2n anh ta c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea3y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i sao khi t\u00f4i v\u1ed1n nhanh v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, th\u1ebf n\u00ean m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-bao-ve-brazil-va-neymar-sau-ky-world-cup-that-vong-421-191694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/kaka-bao-ve-brazil-va-neymar-sau-ky-world-cup-that-vong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-bao-ve-brazil-va-neymar-sau-ky-world-cup-that-vong-421-191694.html\">Kaka b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Samba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil ch\u1ec9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u0169 kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t leo thang, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4500","checkdouble":"191792"},{"date":"20:03 22/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7: Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-227-chelsea-nham-chieu-mo-sao-tre-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7.</h2><h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 227 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 227 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/MU-muon-mua-Kylian-Mbappe-thay-Anthony-Martial-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7:&nbsp;Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Times, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Anthony Martial t\u1eeb Man United. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Eden Hazard mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid, The Blues \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man United \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 Martial 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Bayern c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u1ebb h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Man City d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sport Mediaset kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Chelsea v\u00e0 Barcelona c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man xanh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi c\u1ea3 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Pjanic v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i do Juve v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau sao Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<h2>MU ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n sao tr\u1ebb Rochdale</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man United \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n sao tr\u1ebb Daniel Adshead c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi Rochdale. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League. Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp k\u00edn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i U23 MU v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Pulisic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch sao tr\u1ebb Christian Pulisic. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng n\u00e0y. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pulisic.</div>\r\n<h2>Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Joe Hart \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Hart \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Torino r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 West Ham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Hart v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar m\u1edbi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 12 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-sao-khung-croatia-184-191766.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/07: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-217-choang-voi-muc-gia-kinh-hoang-cua-hang-thai-mu-184-191748.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 21/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4499","checkdouble":"191793"},{"date":"21:08 22/07","title":"Liverpool 1-3 Dortmund: The Kop thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y Klopp \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/liverpool-vs-dortmund-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Christian Pulisic gi\u00fap Dortmund ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool 3-1. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Kop l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Xhedran Shaqiri, Nabil Keita v\u00e0 Alisson \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/23/Liverpool-vs-Dortmund.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac HLV Jurgen Klopp b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u1eafp gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mang theo 29 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 Salah hay Mane. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, The Kop s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Dortmund trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i ICC Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 \u00f4ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 7 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi Dortmund, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Liverpool s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV m\u1edbi Lucien Favre ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n, Liverpool \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi Dortmund. D\u00f9 HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng tung ra s\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Mane, Salah hay t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Kop v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh ra san cua Liverpool duoc danh gia cao hon Dortmund kha nhieu\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Dortmund kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Dortmund kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Clyne, Van Dijk hay Robertson \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Adam Lallana c\u00f2n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Origi ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t, b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn HLV Lucien Favre c\u1ee7a Dortmund kh\u00f4ng tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr nh\u01b0 Gotze, Marco Reus, Pulisic hay Piszczek \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Dortmund m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ph\u00fat 3, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius b\u0103ng ra ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng l\u1ed7i t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Philipp c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, song \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35m v\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Dortmund l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra ngo\u00e0i. Pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i sao Liverpool ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool chu dong choi tan cong ngay sau tieng coi khai cuoc\" title=\"Liverpool ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/la.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n song Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Dortmund trong kho\u1ea3ng 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, b\u1ed9 ba Markovic, Camacho v\u00e0 Origi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Dortmund t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu The Kop kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">R\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Dortmund l\u1ea1i \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Liverpool g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. The Kop l\u00fac n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u1edf trung l\u1ed9 th\u00ec th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng Liverpool b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean.<strong> Ph\u00fat 25, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Robertson th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf.</strong> Trong m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung ve Van Dijk danh dau mo ty so cho Liverpool\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/van.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Dortmund \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u0169ng thanh tho\u00e1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Ph\u00fat 33, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Robertson th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 song Camacho l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 39, Dortmund th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o v\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Dieckmann th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf g\u00f3c h\u1eb9p song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00f4m g\u1ecdn b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Dortmund t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. Nh\u00ecn chung trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Van Dijk gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 sau 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool dan truoc 1-0 sau 45 phut thi dau dau tien\" title=\"Liverpool d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 sau 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/liverpool.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 sau 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00ean ph\u00eda Liverpool, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Origi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n. V\u00e0o s\u00e2n l\u00e0 Gomez, Phillips, Milner, Keita, Sturridge, Klavan, Moreno, Solanke v\u00e0 Woodburn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">B\u00ean ph\u00eda Dortmund ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 Zagadou v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hitz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u00ean ph\u00eda Dortmund l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mario Gotze, Pulisic v\u00e0 Schmelzer.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 49, Sturridge c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u0103ng ngang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o trong, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ojo song \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng The Kop s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 56, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi James Milner th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 ngang.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Dortmund l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool ch\u01a1i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Pulisic hay Gotze ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o. Ph\u00fat 59, Sturridge th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Liverpool l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Woodburn c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Sturridge th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Ojo, nh\u01b0ng trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Dortmund, b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ed9i tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra ngo\u00e0i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sau h\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 n\u00e0y Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. <strong>Ph\u00fat 66, Pulisic b\u1ecb Klavan ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho Dortmund \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh Pulisic d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Karius c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1</strong>.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pulisic go hoa 1-1 cho Dortmund tren cham 11m\" title=\"Pulisic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Dortmund tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/pulisic.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pulisic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Dortmund tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">B\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Pulisic khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u1eeb ph\u00fat 72 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 75, Liverpool c\u00f3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean song Woodburn v\u00e0 Moreno \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. The Kop \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Ph\u00fat 85, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Joe Gomez c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hitz. 4 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Liverpool ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Ph\u00fat 89, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh Gotze chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Pulisic d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1. 3 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Dortmund c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Pulisic, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jacob Bruun Larsen, \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 34 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-1.<br>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dortmund nguoc dong danh bai Liverpool 3-1\" title=\"Dortmund ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool 3-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/thang-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dortmund ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool 3-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>  </strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 1-3 \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Pulisic ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn, anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dortmund v\u1edbi 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>Liverpool: </strong>1 L. Karius, 2 N. Clyne (Phillips, 62'), 32 J. Matip (Gomez, 22'), 4 V. van Dijk (Klavan, 46'), 26 A. Robertson (Moreno, 46'), 20 A. Lallana (Milner, 46'), 50 L. Markovic (Solanke, 46'), 3 Fabinho (Keita, 46'), 64 Rafael Camacho (Ojo, 46'), 48 C. Jones (Woodburn, 46'), 27 D. Origi</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<strong>Dortmund: </strong>35 M. Hitz, 15 J. Toljan (Bockhorn, 46'), 4 A. Diallo, 2 D. Zagadou (Gotze, 46'), 8 N. Sahin (Burnic, 46'), 19 M. Dahoud (Pieper, 46'), 43 D. Boadud (Sergio Gomez, 46'), 7 J. Sancho (Jacob Bruun Larsen, 46'), 20 M. Philipp (Isak, 46'), 27 M. Wolf (Pulisic, 46'), 45 S. Dieckmann (Schmelzer, 46')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4498","checkdouble":"191797"},{"date":"02:37 23/07","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/1/mateo-kovacic-yeu-cau-duoc-roi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mateo Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Mateo-Kovacic-roi-Real-Madrid-cap-ben-Ngoai-hang-Anh-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Kovacic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Kovacic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. Theo Marca, Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu. C\u1ef1u sao Inter \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Los Blancos \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. \u1ede Anh c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan, bao g\u1ed3m hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u00e0 Tottenham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/Sao-khung-Croatia-muon-dut-tinh-voi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</span>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb Los Blancos l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Bernabeu b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Kovacic li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i, Real Madrid nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Marca, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Kovacic, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Italia, Juventus v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Kovacic, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Anh n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real Madrid. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)\u2003</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4497","checkdouble":"191805"},{"date":"06:05 23/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga. Anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, gi\u00fap Colombia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca, Mina l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 t\u1eeb Palmeiras, trung v\u1ec7 cao 1m95 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201ct\u1eed huy\u1ec7t\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Yerry-Mina-sap-roi-Barca-toi-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Clement Lenglet, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1edd m\u1ecbt. Anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde sau Pique, Umtiti, Lenglet v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Vermaelen.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 thi\u00ean h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" title=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fa v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina. HLV Marco Silva c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Jair Mina v\u1ec1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Goodison Park, r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh cho trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mina t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Barcelona. Everton s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Barca s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (17 tri\u1ec7u Euro) c\u00f9ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (11,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Marcel Brands c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111ang tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng l\u1ea1c quan Mina s\u1ebd s\u1edbm gia nh\u1eadp sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-barca-180-191783.html\">T\u1edbi Barca, t\u00e2n binh 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-tien-cu-rabiot-cho-barca-180-191740.html\">Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i thay Iniesta cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4496","checkdouble":"191808"},{"date":"22:37 22/07","title":"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matip tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Cameroon \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Matip bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i theo d\u00f5i The Kop thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lovren v\u00e0 Van Dijk t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 \u0103n \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho Lovren c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a sau. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o 6/8 t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matip s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd v\u1eady, Matip s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Ragnar Klavan cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Van Dijk. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Schalke t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 100% nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian n\u1eefa\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Matip tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. The Kop li\u00ean t\u1ee5c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Fabinho, Alisson Becker c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Shaqiri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ra sao nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu-172-191769.html\">Klopp: MU m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c Liverpool, c\u00f2n Liverpool m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp-172-191760.html\">100% NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nghe tin n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Klopp?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4495","checkdouble":"191801"},{"date":"23:59 22/07","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u00ea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho... Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Christian Pulisic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pulisic<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 174 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson (66.8), Naby Keita (52.75), Fabinho (43), Shaqiri (13.5), Liverpool c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Christian Pulisic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"T\u00f4i th\u00edch Pulisic, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. Pulisic ch\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Anh ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng Pulisic \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 14 \u0111\u1ebfn 15 n\u0103m trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u1edbi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u00e0? T\u00f4i ch\u1ecbu\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Pulisic v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dortmund. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho MU<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Jurgen Klopp t\u1eebng ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch Manchester United ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec Paul Pogba v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Kop l\u1ea1i bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Klopp h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng m\u1eafc quai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n minh cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 th\u1eeba cho Man Utd: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u1ebft ti\u1ec7t b\u1ea1n n\u00f3i, ch\u1eb3ng ai qu\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. T\u00f4i l\u00e0m sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhanh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\"M\u1ed9t tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u th\u1eadt l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Man Utd t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Liverpool:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp-172-191760.html\">100% NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nghe tin n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Klopp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings-172-191735.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-luon-tuong-tuong-minh-se-tro-thanh-gerrard-172-191724.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Gerrard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-172-191696.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ea3nh, n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4494","checkdouble":"191802"},{"date":"02:59 23/07","title":"Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid nh\u1eafm Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo ra \u0111i bu\u1ed9c Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Khi m\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe b\u1ecb h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao th\u00ec Hazard tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 thi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial thay Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial thay Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chelsea-muon-mua-Anthony-Martial-thay-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real c\u00f3 Hazard l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Eden Hazard</span>, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mbappe (165 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (sau Neymar).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Real \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Hazard, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial thay Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/martial-co-tiem-nang-tro-thanh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial thay Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u euro) mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Martial th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Martial th\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leon Bailey c\u1ee7a CLB Bayer Leverkusen c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song The Blues ch\u1ec9 mua ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bundesliga trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Martial.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4493","checkdouble":"191806"}]}